Inexhaustibility.help: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character. Slotting this enhancement into Rest will give the user a chance to recover Hit Points and Endurance at a rapid rate if they've been out of combat for 30 seconds or more. In a PvP zone the player will gain a chance to receive a dramatic boost to regeneration instead of the healing effect triggered by this power. NOTE: Inexhaustibility can only be slotted into Rest and rest does not need to be activated for this power's effect to be triggered.

Small_Critical_Hit_Bonus.help: Boosts your chance to critically hit with your primary powers against players and minions by 2% and boosts your chance to critically hit by 4% against most other enemies.

Large_Critical_Hit_Bonus.help: Boosts your chance to critically hit with your primary powers against players and minions by 3% and boosts your chance to critically hit by 6% against most other enemies.
